appList.title: The Open
appList.description:
The official app of The Open, golf’s oldest and most international Major Championship. The world’s top players return to St Andrews from 12-19 July, 2015 to take their place in history and compete for the iconic Claret Jug. 

The app is available year round and is updated with the latest news as players qualify for The Open. During the Championship, expect up-to-the-minute live scoring, video highlights and an interactive course guide, accompanied by live golf from The Open and @TheOpen RADIO. Coverage of holes 13, 14 and 15 will be available during the Championship along with @TheOpen LIVE, offering you a unique behind the scenes view at the Home of Golf. 

The latest and most relevant updates throughout the Championship will be presented through our dynamic Timeline feature, including news, social media highlights, photos and live updates straight from the course so you don’t miss a shot. (BBC coverage is only available in the UK)

appList.title: MLB.com At Bat
appList.description:
MLB.com At Bat – the #1 source for live baseball – Is the official app of Major League Baseball. 
****At Bat Features****

- App available in Spanish language, requires device language set to Spanish
- Support for Android Auto
- Push Notifications for breaking news, lead changes, and more
- Customize At Bat's home screen to feature your designated favorite team(s) (phone & 7" tablets)
- Favorite team icon home screen widget for one-click access to your favorite team's At Bat homepage (Phones only)
- MLB icon home screen widget for in-progress scores around the league
- Sortable batting, pitching and fielding statistics
- Breaking news, schedules and interactive rosters and players stats for every team


****Subscribe to At Bat Premium to Access Additional Features****

- Watch the Free MLB.TV Game of the Day
- Home and away live radio broadcasts of every game, choose broadcast feeds
- Additional push notifications for in-game highlights and condensed games
- Chromecast support
- See key plays and pivotal moments from every game with Live Look-Ins (No blackout restrictions)
- Video library archive, searchable by player, team or keyword (Phones only)
- Multi-platform live audio access for At Bat Premium subscribers (portable to Mac/PC with a valid MLB.com account)
- Universal support for At Bat Premium subscribers, accessible on Android smartphones and tablets and other supported mobile devices
- Watch every out-of-market game live (requires MLB.TV Premium subscription)
- Access archives to watch 2015 MLB games on-demand (requires MLB.TV Premium subscription)
- Gameday pitch-by-pitch tracking, including realistic ballpark renderings from all 30 MLB ballparks
- Closed captioning availability for MLB.TV live video
- In-progress video highlights


****At Bat Subscription Options***

- Yearly recurring fee of $19.99
- Monthly recurring fee of $2.99
- MLB.TV Premium subscribers receive At Bat Premium features for free.


MLB.com At Bat features live action from the Arizona Diamondbacks, Atlanta Braves, Baltimore Orioles, Boston Red Sox, Chicago Cubs, Chicago White Sox, Cincinnati Reds, Cleveland Indians, Colorado Rockies, Detroit Tigers, Houston Astros, Kansas City Royals, Los Angeles Angels of Anaheim, Los Angeles Dodgers, Miami Marlins, Milwaukee Brewers, Minnesota Twins, New York Mets, New York Yankees, Oakland Athletics, Philadelphia Phillies, Pittsburgh Pirates, St. Louis Cardinals, San Diego Padres, San Francisco Giants, Seattle Mariners, Tampa Bay Rays, Texas Rangers, Toronto Blue Jays and Washington Nationals.

Access At Bat Premium for $2.99 per month or $19.99 annually. You will be automatically billed $2.99 through Google Play every 30 days or $19.99 every 365 days until you cancel your subscription. Your subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. You subscription can be managed and the auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the Google Play Account Settings after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during active subscription period.

appList.title: FOX Sports GO

FOX Sports GO is your exclusive home to live broadcasts of the 2015 FIFA Women’s World Cup! Watch the great network coverage from FOX and FOX Sports 1 for all 52 matches, plus great bonus feeds including Cable Cam, Tactical View, and Match 360. See preview shows for every match, post-match analysis, and nightly wrap-ups. FOX Sports GO is also the only place you can watch the live stream of the 2015 U.S. Open television broadcast! With the main broadcast plus Featured Group, Featured Holes, and U.S. Open 360 coverage, you won’t miss a a drive, chip, or putt!

With FOX Sports GO, you can watch live sports and great shows from FOX Sports. Depending on your TV provider, FOX Sports, FOX Sports 1, FOX Sports 2, your regional FOX Sports Network, FOX College Sports and FOX Deportes may be available.* No matter where you go, take FOX Sports with you on your Android device.

FOX Sports GO features live coverage of great sports:

• NFL (web and tablet only)**

DUE TO LEAGUE RESTRICTIONS, NFL GAMES ARE NOT AVAILABLE IN FOX SPORTS GO ON PHONES.

You can also stream great shows like FOX Sports Live, The Ultimate Fighter, and NASCAR Race Hub.

FOX Sports GO is free to download. All you need to do to watch is sign in with your TV provider credentials. The following major TV providers are current FOX Sports GO partners:

appList.title: FishBrain - Fishing Forecast
appList.description:
NOTHING BEATS REAL ANGLERS WORKING TOGETHER! 
FishBrain is the world's largest community-based fishing app. Join other anglers in your area and contribute to the worlds smartest local fishing forecasts. SEE WHAT'S BITING IN YOUR AREA
• The smart FishBrain Forecast shows what species are biting in your area.
• All forecasts are generated with machine learning algorithms from real catch-data
• Hundreds of thousands of catches are already on FishBrain! And with each new catch FishBrain gets smarter and the forecasts even more accurate!

COMPETITION
• Climb the leaderboards in your favourite fishing location and become King!
• Gather your friends and start a team together and let the battle begin! 

CHOOSE WHAT YOU SHARE
• Choose the privacy level you prefer for every single catch you add. 
• See fishing location and exact position for your own catches even if you choose to hide them from fellow anglers.

FishBrain is all about anglers contributing to and benefiting from the community, so get involved today! 

Note: Continued use of GPS in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.
